=========================================
=    For users of NAMD    on csb.       =
=========================================

In your script add one of the following lines:
(these are increasing version numbers).
module load namd/2.12
module load namd/2.XX

Note that if you include more than one, the last one will override the others.

The usual way to invoke namd is:

charmrun namd2 +p8 molecule.conf > molecule.log


